title: Wage and Salary Disbursements, Distributive Industries, Services, and Government for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1929-1946 (2)--Seasonally Adjusted Data, 1946-1966. Data Are Monthly Totals At Annual Rate. Source: For 1946-1962 Data: Survey Of Current Business, August 1965; For 1963-1966 Data: Survey Of Current Business, July 1966 And Subsequent Issues.

This NBER data series m08274b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 8 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter08.html.
